{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01DbfHembCXoYKjwnh5VX2rQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"That's the root cause. The `rabbitmq-cookie-perpod` secret has:\n- `rabbitmq-0`: `c3VwZXJzZWNyZXRjb29raWU=` = \"supersecretcookie\"\n- `rabbitmq-1`: `c3VwZXJzZWNyZXRjb29raWU=` = \"supersecretcookie\"  \n- `rabbitmq-2`: `ZHJpZnRlZGNvb2tpZQ==` = \"driftedcookie\"\nSo rabbitmq-2 has a mismatched Erlang cookie, which prevents it from authenticating and joining the cluster. The fix requires updating the secret to give rabbitmq-2 the same cookie as the other nodes, but since the init container already baked the wrong cookie into the pod's filesystem, just updating the secret won't be enough — I'll need to restart the pod to pick up the corrected value.\n\nLet me examine how the StatefulSet configures the init container and manages the cookie file on the persistent volume.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1475,"cache_read_input_tokens":37839,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1475},"output_tokens":45,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f6c3cc50-0ae1-4483-aa74-5c8fe22ae47b","uuid":"a402f53b-a93b-4d4a-a0be-99b9ed16c817","request_id":"req_011Cbzr7JQLSSaMtSQ9xCzSf"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01DbfHembCXoYKjwnh5VX2rQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Found the root cause: rabbitmq-2 has a different Erlang cookie (`driftedcookie`) vs nodes 0 and 1 (`supersecretcookie`). Let me examine the StatefulSet to understand how cookies are mounted."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1475,"cache_read_input_tokens":37839,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1475},"output_tokens":45,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f6c3cc50-0ae1-4483-aa74-5c8fe22ae47b","uuid":"ee3e8483-fc4c-4a72-a42c-cec3b7090bc0","request_id":"req_011Cbzr7JQLSSaMtSQ9xCzSf"}
