{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":134359,"duration_api_ms":109564,"ttft_ms":2334,"ttft_stream_ms":1494,"time_to_request_ms":39,"num_turns":22,"result":"The cluster is fully restored. Here's a summary of what happened and what was done:\n\n**Root cause:** The Secret `rabbitmq-cookie-perpod` had a deliberate fault — `rabbitmq-2` was given the Erlang cookie `driftedcookie` while nodes 0 and 1 had `supersecretcookie`. The init container (`copy-cookie`) copies the pod's named entry from this Secret into `/var/lib/rabbitmq/.erlang.cookie` at startup. With a mismatched cookie, Erlang's distributed protocol rejects all inter-node communication, so rabbitmq-2 bootstrapped as an isolated standalone cluster instead of joining.\n\n**What was done (all native Kubernetes resources, no CRDs):**\n\n1. **Patched the Secret** — changed `rabbitmq-2`'s cookie entry to `supersecretcookie` (same base64 as nodes 0 and 1)\n2. **Deleted the pod** — the StatefulSet controller recreated it; the init container ran again and copied the now-correct cookie\n3. **Reset + joined** inside the pod:\n   - `rabbitmqctl stop_app` — stopped the app layer (Erlang VM stayed up)\n   - `rabbitmqctl reset` — wiped the standalone mnesia cluster identity from node 2's PVC\n   - `rabbitmqctl join_cluster rabbit@rabbitmq-0...` — joined to the existing cluster\n   - `rabbitmqctl start_app` — started the app layer back up\n\n**Result:** All 3 nodes are now Disk Nodes, all Running, no Alarms, no Network Partitions.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"f6c3cc50-0ae1-4483-aa74-5c8fe22ae47b","total_cost_usd":0.39869905,"usage":{"input_tokens":19,"cache_creation_input_tokens":30723,"cache_read_input_tokens":654366,"output_tokens":5754,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":30723,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":388,"cache_read_input_tokens":45894,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1862,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1862},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":706,"outputTokens":21,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.000811,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":19,"outputTokens":5754,"cacheReadInputTokens":654366,"cacheCreationInputTokens":30723,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.39788805,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"333ca12e-b181-4969-99c5-2afc939246ab"}
